        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1459607535" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2848064135394613304">Such a great book. My second book by Lahiri and it did not disappoint. Her writing is beautiful and lyrical. I did see this movie many times as it is a favorite. Even though I know the story, the book seemed new to me. The audio version was so easy to listen to. I an fascinated by Indian culture and love reading about it. I can see myself reading this one over and over again and will be watching the movie again very soon. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


