<li class='cover' id='bookCover_1768603'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/1768603.The_White_Tiger"><img alt="The White Tiger" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1347754998l/1768603._SX98_.jpg" />
